cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the coordination of highly automated vehicles in road intersections, which is a problem in robotics and control systems. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves communication requirements and decision-making, which fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), respectively. The use of nonlinear model predictive control and optimization methods suggests cs.MA (Machine Learning) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as possible sub-categories.
